{"tid":97032,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"點解搵旅伴會咁撚艱難","createTime":"2017-01-27T10:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T22:52:55.000Z","uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28b38d22ae81ed13d93ddc4688b5bed8f7a8d340","tid":97032,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"本身已經毒撚冇乜朋友<br />\n就算去日本台灣都好難搵到朋友一齊去<br />\n去印度呀中亞呀之類既落後地方更加係mission impossible <br />\n問左好多朋友都冇人肯同我去<br />\n偏偏e d地方公共交通唔發達，好多時要租車包車<br />\n唔夾錢租車包車如同燒錢<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367cacedab7b196ce14184ab2a5476be55a04b69","tid":97032,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"一齊去南美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c22533e656d9c282488242de0d64fbdc6bc1133","tid":97032,"uid":43804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:52:35.000Z","msg":"我明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add802d92455bb3ffebd4b4f6050295446ef421e","tid":97032,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:57:23.000Z","msg":"去到先搵囉<br />\n岩玩咪keep in touch<br />\n唔岩玩咪拜拜"},{"pid":"18d10b4356c0183b7fe155281ec2515f6ba084f8","tid":97032,"uid":79927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊去南美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南美公共交通配套反而好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f61362b63a5503f32cebbeff1795de9cf60ed5","tid":97032,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一齊去南美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南美公共交通配套反而好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngo together"},{"pid":"952b79468